fields.title: Modern Luxury Villa
fields.description: Stunning 5-bedroom villa with infinity pool and panoramic mountain views. Features include gourmet chef's kitchen, home theater, wine cellar, and complete smart home automation. High-end finishes throughout.

fields.title: Downtown Loft Apartment
fields.description: Spacious 2-bedroom loft in the heart of downtown Manhattan. Exposed brick walls, high ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows. Walking distance to restaurants, theaters, and subway. Building amenities include doorman, gym, and rooftop terrace.

fields.title: Charming Family Home
fields.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom home in quiet, family-friendly neighborhood. Large backyard perfect for kids and pets. Updated kitchen with granite counters and stainless appliances. Excellent schools nearby. Move-in ready!

fields.title: Beachfront Luxury Condo
fields.description: Spectacular 3-bedroom oceanfront condo with breathtaking views. Resort-style amenities including heated pool, spa, fitness center, and 24-hour concierge. Private beach access. Fully furnished and turnkey.

fields.title: Cozy Starter Home
fields.description: Perfect for first-time buyers! Charming 3-bedroom home with updated kitchen and bathrooms. Hardwood floors, new roof, and energy-efficient windows. Fenced backyard and detached garage.

fields.title: Rustic Mountain Retreat
fields.description: Secluded 2-bedroom cabin on 5 acres with stunning mountain and forest views. Wood-burning fireplace, wraparound deck, and hot tub. Perfect weekend getaway or vacation rental opportunity.

fields.title: Modern Studio in Tech District
fields.description: Efficient studio apartment in the heart of the tech district. Perfect for young professionals. Modern finishes, in-unit washer/dryer, and building amenities. Walk to major tech companies and public transit.

fields.title: Waterfront Estate with Private Dock
fields.description: Magnificent 6-bedroom waterfront estate on 2 acres. Private dock, boat house, and 200 feet of water frontage. Gourmet kitchen, master suite with spa bath, and guest house. Truly one-of-a-kind property.

fields.title: Prime Retail Space in Shopping District
fields.description: High-traffic retail location in premier shopping district. 3,000 sq ft of open space with large storefront windows. Perfect for restaurant, boutique, or professional office. Ample parking and excellent visibility.

fields.title: Contemporary 3-Story Townhouse
fields.description: Stunning modern townhouse with rooftop deck and city views. Open floor plan, chef's kitchen with quartz counters, master suite with walk-in closet. Attached 2-car garage and private entrance.

fields.title: Residential Building Lot - Prime Location
fields.description: Exceptional 2-acre lot in rapidly developing area. Utilities available at street, ready to build. Approved for single-family home up to 5,000 sq ft. Mountain views and convenient to shopping and schools.

fields.title: Single-Story Ranch Home
fields.description: Well-maintained 3-bedroom ranch on large corner lot. Vaulted ceilings, updated kitchen and baths, new HVAC system. Mature landscaping and covered patio. Great neighborhood with low HOA fees.

fields.title: Restored Historic Brownstone
fields.description: Beautifully restored 4-bedroom brownstone in historic district. Original architectural details including crown molding, hardwood floors, and marble fireplaces. Modern kitchen and updated systems while maintaining period charm.

fields.title: Luxury Villa on Golf Course
fields.description: Spectacular 4-bedroom villa overlooking 18th hole. Gourmet kitchen, wine room, home office, and resort-style pool. Golf cart garage and membership available. Guard-gated community with clubhouse.

fields.title: Penthouse with Panoramic City Views
fields.description: Stunning 3-bedroom penthouse on the 40th floor. Floor-to-ceiling windows with 360-degree city views. Private elevator, chef's kitchen with Sub-Zero appliances, and 2,000 sq ft terrace. Building concierge and valet parking.
